name: H=N Community BLOCK °05
description:
_______H=N Community BLOCK °05__________
This OBJKT documents the first realtime participatory design activities at the H=N BLOCK platform of OBJKT#187962. H=N BLOCK celebrates the H=N Community, allowing multiple users to contribute to a multi-subjective & multi-objective collaborative whole, an open architecture of collaborative objects. These shared blocks are visible as long as a visitor is Here And Now. Activities on 08.08.2021 were captured, 2607 BLOCKs were instantiated by 18 curious artists and visitors of the H=N Community, receiving this OBJKT is an air-drop. 
_________________
H=N BLOCK by Alexander Grasser, 2021
